quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  70,19,Mu by’ukuri umuntu yaremanywe ukutihangana
  70,20,"Iyo ikibi kimugezeho, ariheba cyane"
  70,21,"Naho icyiza cyamugeraho, akaba umunyabugugu cyane"
  70,22,Uretse abakora iswala
  70,23,Ba bandi bahozaho iswala zabo
  70,24,Na ba bandi bagena umugabane uzwi (Zakat) mu mitungo yabo
  70,25,Wagenewe usaba n’uwiyumanganyije (nyamara akeneye ubufasha)
  70,26,Na ba bandi bemera ko umunsi w’ibihembo ari ukuri
  70,27,Na ba bandi batinya ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo
  70,28,Kubera ko mu by’ukuri ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo nta n’umwe wakwizera ko bitamugeraho
  70,29,Na ba bandi barinda ubwambure bwabo (ubusambanyi)
  70,30,Uretse ku bagore babo cyangwa se ku bo bafiteho ububasha (abaja). Mu by’ukuri bo ntibabigayirwa
  70,31,"Ariko abazashaka (kwinezeza) ku batari abo (bavuzwe), rwose abo bazaba batandukiriye"
  70,32,Na ba bandi barinda ibyo baragijwe ndetse bakubahiriza n’amasezerano yabo
  70,33,Na ba bandi batanga ubuhamya bw’ukuri
  70,34,Na ba bandi bahozaho iswala zabo (ku bihe byagenwe)
  70,35,Abo bazajya mu busitani (Ijuru) kandi bubashywe
  70,36,"None se ni iyihe mpamvu ituma abahakanyi bakugana (yewe Muhamadi) bihuta (bashaka kukumva, kandi batakwemera)"
  70,37,(Bicaye) mu matsinda iburyo n’ibumoso bwawe
  70,38,Ese buri wese muri bo ararikiye kuzinjizwa mu Ijuru ryuje ingabire
  70,39,Ntabwo ari ko bimeze! Mu by’ukuri twabaremye tubakomoye mu byo bazi (ariko banga kwemera)
  70,40,"Bityo, ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba bwose n’Uburengerazuba bwose, ko rwose dushoboye"
  70,41,"Kubasimbuza abeza kubarusha, kandi ntibyatunanira"
  70,42,"Bityo, bareke bavuge ibidafite umumaro, banikinire kugeza ubwo bazahura n’umunsi wabo basezeranyijwe"
  70,43,"Umunsi bazasohoka mu mva zabo bihuta, nk’uko bihutaga bagana amabuye ashinze (ibigirwamana byabo)"
  70,44,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), batwikiriwe n’ugusuzugurika. Uwo ni wo munsi bajyaga basezeranywa"
  71,1,Mu by’ukuri twohereje Nuhu ku bantu be (tugira tuti) “Burira abantu bawe mbere y’uko ibihano bibabaza bibageraho.”
  71,2,(Nuhu) aravuga ati “Bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri njye ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara
  71,3,"(Ubaburira ko) mugomba kugaragira Allah (wenyine), mukanamugandukira kandi mukanyumvira"
  71,4,"(Ibyo nimubikora, Allah) azabababarira ibyaha byanyu, anabahe kubaho kugeza igihe cyagenwe. Mu by’ukuri iyo igihe ntarengwa (cyo gupfa) Allah yagennye kigeze nticyongerwa, iyaba mwari mubizi.”"
  71,5,(Nuhu) aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Mu by’ukuri nahamagariye abantu banjye ijoro n’amanywa (ko bagomba kugaragira Imana imwe)”
  71,6,Ariko uguhamagara kwanjye nta cyo kwabongereye uretse guhunga (ukuri)
  71,7,"Kandi mu by’ukuri buri uko nabahamagariraga (kwemera Imana imwe) kugira ngo ubababarire ibyaha byabo, bashyiraga intoki mu matwi, bakitwikira imyambaro, bagatsimbarara ndetse bakanibona cyane"
  71,8,Hanyuma kandi nabahamagaye ku mugaragaro
  71,9,Hanyuma nanabatangarije (mu ijwi riranguruye) ndetse nanababwira mu ibanga
  71,10,"Narababwiye nti “Nimusabe imbabazi Nyagasani wanyu, mu by’ukuri ni We uhebuje mu kubabarira ibyaha.”"
  71,11,(Kugira ngo) azaboherereze imvura nyinshi (ihagije)
  71,12,"Anabongerere imitungo n’urubyaro, abahe ubusitani (Ijuru) ndetse abahe n’imigezi (yaryo)"
  71,13,Kubera iki mudaha Allah icyubahiro kimukwiye
  71,14,Kandi ari We wabaremye mu byiciro (bitandukanye)
  71,15,Ese ntimubona uburyo Allah yaremye ibirere birindwi bigerekeranye
  71,16,Hanyuma akabishyiramo ukwezi akakugira urumuri ndetse n’izuba akarigira itara
  71,17,Kandi Allah yabakujije abakuye mu butaka nk’ibimera
  71,18,Hanyuma azabubasubizamo (igihe cyo gupfa) ndetse anabubasohoremo (ku munsi w’izuka)
  71,19,Kandi Allah ni We wabagiriye isi nk’isaso
  71,20,Kugira ngo muyigendeho (mugendera) mu mayira magari
  71,21,"Nuhu aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Mu by’ukuri (abantu banjye) banyigometseho, banakurikira uwo imitungo n’abana bitagize icyo byongerera uretse igihombo.”"
  71,22,Nuko (abantu be) bacura umugambi mubi (wo kubangamira ubutumwa bwe)
  71,23,"Baranavuga bati “Rwose ntimuzareke imana zanyu, kandi ntimuzareke (kugaragira) Wadan, Suwa’a, Yagutha, Ya’uqa ndetse na Nasra"
  71,24,"(Nuhu aravuga ati) “Kandi rwose (ibyo bigirwamana) byayobeje benshi. Bityo (yewe Allah), ntuzagire ikindi wongerera ababangikanyamana kitari ubuyobe.”"
  71,25,"Kubera ibyaha byabo, bararohamishijwe kandi bazinjizwa mu muriro, ndetse ntibazigera babona ababatabara batari Allah"
  71,26,Nuhu aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Ntuzagire n’umwe muri aba bahakanyi usiga ku isi.”
  71,27,"Kuko mu by’ukuri nubareka, bazayobya abagaragu bawe, kandi ntibazigera babyara abandi batari abanyabyaha b’abahakanyi"
  71,28,"(Nuhu aravuga ati) “Nyagasani wanjye! Mbabarira, njye n’ababyeyi banjye, n’uzinjira mu nzu yanjye ari umwemeramana, ndetse n’abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi. Kandi ntuzagire ikindi wongerera abahakanyi kitari ukorama.”"